  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="4" name="MSG_004_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 2 51 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 5 0 0}The enemy is acting strangely. I have a bad feeling about this.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_005_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}But if we don't go after it, we're gonna lose it![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 51 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}{f 4 1}, you're in command right now.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 51 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}What do you think of the situation?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="7" name="SEL_007_0_0" type="Selection">
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}We should be careful.]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}We should go after it.]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}I don't know.]]></Option>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="8" name="MSG_008_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 51 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}I agree.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 51 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}It would be dangerous to chase after it blindly.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="9" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 2 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}So what if it's dangerous!? We can't just stand here and let it get away![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="10" name="MSG_010_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 51 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}But why did it flee after revealing itself? I can't make sense of it.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 51 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}Just be careful.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="11" name="MSG_011_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 51 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}I don't have any more information, either.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 51 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}Just be careful.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="12" name="MSG_012_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 2 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 16 0 0}We can beat that thing no problem![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 2 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 17 0 0}Hell, I'll do it myself![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="13" name="MSG_013_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 2 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 18 0 0}Junpei! Wait![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="14" name="MSG_014_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 2 51 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 19 0 0}Watch out! Behind you![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
